21
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:07,359
Northern Chu won against Eastern Xia
with the help of His Highness.

22
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:09,840
Hence, Hua Nongying, the crown prince
hold a banquet to appreciate his effort

23
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:12,560
and invited him to travel
in Northern Chu for a day or two.

24
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:14,000
His Highness will be back in no time.

25
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,799
He seems to enjoy having fun there

26
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:18,040
instead of coming back for you quickly.

27
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:21,079
(Yu Longyuan can't wait
to return earlier,)

28
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,879
(how could he have the mood
to go sightseeing?)

29
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,159
(Wushuang's lie)

30
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,760
(is so clumsy.)

31
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,400
Well.

32
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:31,760
I get it.

33
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,280
All right.

34
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:41,140
(One month later)

35
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,879
