42
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,040
We dare not defy her order.

43
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:58,879
Jinghong.

44
00:01:59,280 --> 00:01:59,680
Open the door.

45
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,319
A mere wooden door

46
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,879
