59
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,639
Have you

60
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,960
made up your mind?

61
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:45,439
I will marry Yu Heng.

62
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,520
