of marrying me.

65
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,280
You're not going to put the gown on
and proceed marriage ritual

66
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,439
before Uncle Thirteen shows up.

67
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,879
But if he comes,

68
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,639
you will leave with him
without hesitation.

69
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:25,560
Yes, I will.

70
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,000
You get that right.

71
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,479
I never wanted to marry you.

72
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:31,159
